snippet.title: Blood Bowl gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Blood Bowl, Dos PC game produced by Destiny Software in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/blood-bowl/120/
A futuristic football simulation that mixes action and tactics in a unique (and brutal) way.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
